  "title": "New Slide 8",
  "html": "\n\n  <div id=\"slide-scaler\" style=\"transform: scale(1); margin-left: 207px; margin-top: 0px;\"><section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font-body); padding: 2rem; overflow: hidden;\">\n  <style>\n    .slide {\n      --delay-1: 0.2s;\n      --delay-2: 0.4s;\n      --delay-3: 0.6s;\n    }\n    .slide-content {\n      width: 100%;\n      max-width: 800px;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 2rem;\n    }\n    .slide-title {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);\n      color: var(--text);\n      text-align: center;\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n      position: relative;\n    }\n    .slide-title::after {\n      content: '';\n      display: block;\n      width: 60px;\n      height: 4px;\n      background: var(--accent);\n      margin: 0.5rem auto;\n      box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-glow);\n    }\n    .concept-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      gap: 1.5rem;\n    }\n    .concept-card {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      padding: 1.5rem;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    .concept-card:hover {\n      border-color: var(--accent);\n      transform: translateY(-5px);\n    }\n    .card-label {\n      color: var(--accent);\n      font-weight: bold;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      font-size: 0.8rem;\n      letter-spacing: 0.1rem;\n      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n      display: block;\n    }\n    .card-text {\n      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n    }\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      animation: revealIn 0.6s forwards ease-out;\n      animation-delay: var(--delay);\n    }\n    @keyframes revealIn {\n      to {\n        opacity: 1;\n        transform: translateY(0);\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-content\">\n    <h1 class=\"slide-title reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: var(--delay-1);\">New Slide 8</h1>\n    \n    <div class=\"concept-grid\">\n      <div class=\"concept-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: var(--delay-2);\">\n        <span class=\"card-label\">Core Principle</span>\n        <p class=\"card-text\">\n          <strong>Key point 1:</strong> Implementation of the primary concept focusing on scalability and modular architecture to ensure long-term maintainability.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"concept-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: var(--delay-3);\">\n        <span class=\"card-label\">Technical Impact</span>\n        <p class=\"card-text\">\n          <strong>Key point 2:</strong> Optimization of performance metrics by reducing overhead and streamlining the data flow between decoupled components.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section></div>\n\n  <!-- Prism Core & Languages -->\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n\n\n",
